@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Login as ADMIN (Authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/demo/login
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{$dotenv ADMIN_EMAIL}}",
  "password": "{{$dotenv ADMIN_PASSWORD}}"
}

##### The following endpoints require an Admin Login first (above)
##### One Login is enough to test all endpoints

### Get all conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/demo/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_KEY}}

### Get conversation by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/demo/conversations/bd1151f9-b562-46f2-a607-cd3aaac1c4dd
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_KEY}}

### Create conversation
POST {{baseUrl}}/demo/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Title",
  "created_by": "demo"
}

### Update conversation
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/demo/conversations/269be190-6475-4969-a55c-c733081120de
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Title"
}

### Delete conversation
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/demo/conversations/269be190-6475-4969-a55c-c733081120de
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json
